title: Linda Eder - Linda Eder (1991)
description:

This is Linda Eder&#039;s first album.  It is a true find for all music lovers. You can just listen to this recording over and over again. In fact, I have. Eder&#039;s voice as well as the music and lyrics are brilliant! You can&#039;t beat this! I love "Vienna," and smile every time I hear it.  I highly recommend "Before I Fall" - gives me goose bumps every time.
